Services

Max's Golf Souvenirs is an online golf subscription platform. We send you monthly packages containing brand new golfing equipment to keep you up to date on the newest gear in the game.

Timeless Shopping

Our company will deliver new equipment every month. No need to spend valuable time shopping for new equipment.

Order Online

Subscribe to our monthly packages of state-of-the-art golf equipment from the comfort of your home.

Secure Shipping

Our packages will arrive securely to your doorstep within 3-5 business days. No shipping fees included!

About

  • 2003-2012

    Our Humble Beginnings

    Our founder, Max, came from a family that loved golf. As a young child, he designed and collected golf equipment wherever he could. He loved it so much that he began selling these products to friends and family.

  • March 2012

    An Agency is Born

    The demand for Max's equipment grew, so he decided to expand his target clients. Max's Gold Souvenirs, an online golf shop, was officially born.

  • December 2015

    Monthly Deliveries

    With such high demand, Max's Golf Souvenirs expanded beyond just Max and the company skyrocketed.

  • July 2022

    Today

    Max's Golf Souvenirs is continuing to expand thanks to your help. We appreciate your support.

Golf Tees

Clubs

For any category of club you need

Handcrafted from the finest, we offer over 50 different variations of each type of club: drivers, woods, hybrids, long irons, mid irons, short irons, pitching wedges, approach wedges, sand wedges, and lob wedges.

Polos
